Enum SpreadSpectrum

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SpreadSpectrum>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<SpreadSpectrum>

    public enum SpreadSpectrum
extends java.lang.Enum<SpreadSpectrum>
    This enum describes nodes selection for PopularityWalker. PLAIN: all nodes within initial spread have equal chances to be picked. PROPORTIONAL: each node will have chance to be picked equal to it's popularity proportion within spread.
